        <item>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fuel Choice and Deregulation Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill revises requirements governing the use of alternative fuels in vehicles, including to </p> <ul> <li>allow certain aftermarket conversions of motor vehicles to alternative fuel operation without certification, </li> <li>ban the Environmental Protection Agency from prohibiting or controlling biomass fuel, and</li> <li>revise the Corporate Average Fuel Economy standards with respect to fuel choice enabling vehicles.</li> </ul>]]></text>
